1:21:08.646 --> 1:21:10.953
Let's get in here. Good.

1:21:10.996 --> 1:21:12.563
All right.

1:21:12.606 --> 1:21:14.260
-Sit right here, okay?
-Okay.

1:21:14.304 --> 1:21:16.175
-All right?
-Okay.

